READ ME - gg_bunker_arena_jon

----------------------------------------------------

BUNKER ARENA
BY JON

----------------------------------------------------

DESCRITPTION:
A small sized gungame map featuring two bunkers inside an enclosed area and an underground
building connecting the two.  Both teams start inside their bunkers and can either fight
aboveground or underground.  Each path leads to the opposing team's bunker and each path
features plenty of objects to hide behind.

----------------------------------------------------

INSTALLATION:
Simply place both the .bsp and .nav files into your map folder.  Your map folder is located
here: C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\(your account name)\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

----------------------------------------------------
